## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1772">Номер паспорта Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1772">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1773">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1773">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1774">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1774">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1775">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1775">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1776">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1776">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1777">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1777">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1778">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1778">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1779">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1779">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1780">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1780">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1781">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1781">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1782">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1782">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1783">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1783">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1784">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1784">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1785">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1785">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1786">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1786">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1798">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1798">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1799">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1799">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1806">Номер банковского счета в Канаде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1806">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1807">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1807">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1808">7 или 12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1808">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1809">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1809">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1810">Номер учетной записи Банка Канады — 7 или 12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1810">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1811">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1811">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1812">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1812">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1813">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1813">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1814">три цифры OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1814">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1815">нулевое значение "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1815">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1816">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1816">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1817">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1817">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1818">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1818">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1819">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1819">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1820">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1820">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1821">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1821">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1822">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1822">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1823">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1823">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1824">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1824">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1825">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1825">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1826">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1826">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1850">Номер водительских прав в Канаде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1850">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1851">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1851">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1852">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1852">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1853">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1853">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1854">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1854">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1855">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1855">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1856">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1856">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1857">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1857">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-1858">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1858">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1859">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1859">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1860">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1860">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-1861">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1861">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1997">Номер службы здравоохранения Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1997">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-1998">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1998">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="72060-1999">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-1999">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2000">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2000">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2001">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2001">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2002">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2002">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2003">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2003">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2004">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2004">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2005">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2005">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2006">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2006">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2007">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2007">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2010">personal health number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2010">personal health number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2013">speciality services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2013">speciality services</span></span>

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2019">Номер паспорта Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2019">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2020">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2020">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2021">два верхних буквы с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2021">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2022">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2022">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2023">два верхних буквы с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2023">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2024">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2024">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2025">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2025">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2026">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2026">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2027">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2027">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2028">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2028">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2029">Найдено ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number Keyword_passport или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2029">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2030">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2030">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2031">Keyword_canada_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2031">Keyword_canada_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2032">canadian citizenship</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2032">canadian citizenship</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2033">canadian passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2033">canadian passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2034">passport application</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2034">passport application</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2035">passport photos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2035">passport photos</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2036">certified translator</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2036">certified translator</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2037">canadian citizens</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2037">canadian citizens</span></span>

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2059">Идентификационный номер личного здоровья Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2059">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2060">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2060">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2061">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2061">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2062">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2062">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2063">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2063">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2064">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2064">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2065">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2065">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2066">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2066">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2067">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2067">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2068">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2068">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2069">Найдены по крайней мере два Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2069">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2102">Номер социального страхования Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2102">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2103">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2103">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2104">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2104">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2105">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2105">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2106">Форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2106">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2107">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2107">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2108">дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2108">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2109">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2109">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2110">дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2110">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2111">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2111">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2112">Unformatted: nine digits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2112">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2113">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2113">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2114">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2114">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2115">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2115">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2116">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2116">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2117">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2117">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2118">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2118">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="72060-2119">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2119">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="72060-2120">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2120">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="72060-2121">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2121">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2122">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2122">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2123">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2123">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2124">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2124">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2125">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2125">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2126">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2126">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2151">Номер удостоверения личности в Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2151">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2152">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2152">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2153">семь-восемь цифр плюс делимитеры контрольная цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2153">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2154">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2154">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2155">семь-восемь цифр плюс делимитеры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2155">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2156">от одной до двух цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2156">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2157">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2157">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2158">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2158">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2159">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2159">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2160">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2160">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2161">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2161">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2162">одна цифра или буква (не чувствительная к делу), которая является проверяемой цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2162">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2163">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2164">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2164">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2165">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2166">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2166">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2167">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2167">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2168">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2168">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2169">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2169">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2170">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2170">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2171">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2171">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2172">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2172">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2209">Номер удостоверения резидента Китая (PRC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2209">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2210">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2210">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2211">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2211">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2212">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2212">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2213">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2213">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2214">шесть цифр, которые являются адресным кодом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2214">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2215">восемь цифр в форме YYYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2215">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2216">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2216">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2217">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2217">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2218">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2218">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2219">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2219">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2220">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2220">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2221">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2221">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2222">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2222">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2223">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2223">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2224">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2224">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2225">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2225">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2226">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2226">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2227">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2227">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2228">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2228">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2229">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2229">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2230">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2230">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2231">PRC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2231">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2232">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2232">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2233">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2233">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2234">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2234">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2235">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2235">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2236">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2236">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2237">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2237">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2238">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2238">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2239">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2239">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2240">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2240">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2241">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2241">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2242">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (dddd), и которые должны пройти тест Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2242">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2243">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2243">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2244">Сложный и надежный шаблон, который обнаруживает карты всех крупных брендов по всему миру, включая карты Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карточки для посетителей.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2244">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2245">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2245">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2246">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2246">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2247">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2247">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2248">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2248">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2249">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2249">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2250">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2250">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="72060-2251">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2251">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="72060-2252">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2252">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="72060-2253">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2253">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2254">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2254">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2255">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2255">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2256">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2256">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2257">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2257">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2258">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2258">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_cc_verification"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2259">Keyword_cc_verification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2259">Keyword_cc_verification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2260">card verification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2260">card verification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2261">card identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2261">card identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2262">cvn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2262">cvn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2263">cid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2263">cid</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2517">Номер водительских прав в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2517">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2518">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2518">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2519">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2519">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2520">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2520">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2521">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2521">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2522">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2522">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2523">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2523">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2524">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2524">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2525">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2525">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2526">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2526">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2527">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2527">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2651">Номер удостоверения личности в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2651">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="72060-2652">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере национальной идентификации ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2652">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72060-2653">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2653">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2654">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2654">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2655">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2655">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2656">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2656">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2657">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2657">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2658">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2658">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2659">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2659">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2660">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2660">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2661">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2661">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2662">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2662">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2663">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2663">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2694">Номер паспорта Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2694">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2695">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2695">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2696">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2696">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2697">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2697">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2698">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2698">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2699">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2699">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2700">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2700">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2701">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2701">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2702">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2702">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2703">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2703">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2704">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2704">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2705">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2705">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2706">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2706">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2707">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2707">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2708">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2708">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2722">broj putovnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2722">broj putovnice</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2726">Личный идентификационный номер (OIB) в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2726">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2727">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2727">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2728">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2728">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2729">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2729">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2730">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2730">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2731">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2731">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2732">окончательная цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2732">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2733">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2733">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2734">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2734">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2735">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2735">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2736">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2736">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2737">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2737">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2738">Ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2738">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2739">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2739">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2740">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2740">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2741">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2741">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2742">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2742">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2773">Номер лицензии для водителей Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2773">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2774">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2774">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2775">12 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2775">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2776">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2776">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2777">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2777">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2778">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2778">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2779">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2779">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2780">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2780">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2781">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2782">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2782">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2783">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2783">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2913">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2913">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2914">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2914">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2915">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2915">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2916">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2916">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2917">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2917">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2918">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2918">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2919">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2919">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2920">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2920">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2921">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2921">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2922">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2922">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2923">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2923">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2924">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2924">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2933">Номер паспорта Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2933">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2934">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2934">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2935">одна буква с 6-8 цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2935">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2936">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2936">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2937">одна буква с шестью или восемью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2937">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2938">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2938">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2939">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2939">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2940">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2940">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2941">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2941">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2942">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2942">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2943">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2943">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2944">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате DD/MM/YYYY или найдено ключевое слово `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2944">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2945">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2945">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2946">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2946">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2947">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2947">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2976">Идентификационный номер налога на Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2976">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="72060-2977">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2977">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2978">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2978">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2979">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2979">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2980">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2980">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2981">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2981">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2982">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2982">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2983">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2983">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2984">восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2984">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2985">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2985">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2986">восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2986">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2987">"0" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2987">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2988">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2988">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2989">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2989">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2990">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2990">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2991">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2991">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2992">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2992">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-2993">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2993">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2994">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2994">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2995">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2995">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="72060-2996">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2996">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-2997">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2997">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-2999">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-2999">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3000">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3000">tax id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3003">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3003">tax identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3006">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3006">tax number</span></span>

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-3025">Номер чешского водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3025">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-3026">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3026">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-3027">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3027">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-3028">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3028">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-3029">восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3029">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3030">буква "E" (не в случае)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3030">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3031">письмо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3031">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3032">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3032">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3033">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3033">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-3034">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3034">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-3035">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3035">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="72060-3036">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3036">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72060-3037">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3037">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3038">Обычное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3038">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="72060-3039">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72060-3039">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```
